text: Gonystylus macrophyllus is a species of plant in the family Thymelaeaceae. It is native to Indonesia, Malaysia, the Nicobar Islands, Papua New Guinea, East Timor, the Solomon Islands, and possibly the Philippines. ==References== macrophyllus Category:Flora of Malesia Category:Flora of Papuasia Category:Flora of the Andaman and Nicobar Islands Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
